(27,'Kettlebell swing','The kettlebell swing is a popular lower-body exercise emphasizing the hamstrings, glutes, and back muscles. It is often used to train explosive power, for aerobic or cardiovascular conditioning, in circuit training, or as an accessory movement for the deadlift.','Strength','Abdominals','Kettlebells','Intermediate',NULL,NULL),
