(1471,'Close-Grip Front Lat Pulldown','The close-grip pull-down is a variation on the lat pull-down, acable-based exercise machine that’s ubiquitous in gyms around the world. This back builder is easy to learn and highly effective, allowing for variable resistance depending on where you place the pin in the stack.','Strength','Lats','Cable','Intermediate',8.8,'Average'),
