(2415,'FYR Air Ball Plus Medicine Ball Jumping Sprawl','The medicine ball air ball to jumping sprawl is a series of bodyweight and medicine ball movement strung together into a single sequence. They collectively target virtually every muscle in the body, as well as seriously challenging the cardiovascular system. It can be a single-movement workout if done for high reps, or part of a larger circuit workout.','Strength','Quadriceps','Medicine Ball','Intermediate',NULL,NULL),
