(2546,'Dumbbell external shoulder rotation','The dumbbell external shoulder rotation is a lightweight dumbbell exercise intended to maintain the health of the shoulder joints, including the rotator cuffs. It is often used as a warm-up or prehab for a shoulder or chest-focused workout with lots of pressing.','Strength','Shoulders','Dumbbell','Intermediate',8.5,'Average'),
