(2575,'Dumbbell hang snatch','The dumbbell hang snatch is an explosive exercise that builds full-body power and targets the muscles of the hips, back, and shoulders. Performing the movement from the hang position, rather than from the ground, emphasizes explosive hip and upper-body power. It can be performed for low reps with a focus on power and speed, or for higher reps to build muscle or as part of a metabolic conditioning circuit.','Strength','Shoulders','Dumbbell','Intermediate',NULL,NULL),
